   <concept id="DFARS_252.225-7041" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3">
      <title>
         <ph props="autonumber">252.225-7041</ph> Correspondence in English.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause">
         <p>As prescribed in 
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly" base="DFARS-225.1103" href="225.1103.dita#DFARS_225.1103">225.1103</xref>
            (2), use the following clause:</p>
         <p outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps">CORRESPONDENCE IN ENGLISH (JUN 1997)</p>
         <p>The Contractor shall ensure that all contract correspondence that is addressed to the United States Government is submitted in English or with an English translation.</p>
         <p outputclass="Endofclause">(End of clause)</p>
      </conbody>
